    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 17th level, you can use your <strong>action </strong>to activate an aura of sunlight that lasts for 1 minute or until you dismiss it using another action. You emit bright light in a 60-foot radius and dim light 30 feet beyond that. Your enemies in the bright light have <strong>disadvantage </strong>on saving throws against any spell that deals fire or radiant damage.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Note: This feature's radius is set to 30 feet to indicate the radius in which enemies should have disadvantage on saving throws</em></p>\n</section>",
